2
00:09:07.297 --> 00:09:09.091
<b>Hello. it's your father.</b>

3
00:09:09.466 --> 00:09:10.884
<b>Call me right away.</b>

4
00:09:37.327 --> 00:09:38.537
<b>She's your sister.</b>

5
00:09:39.580 --> 00:09:41.123
<b>Isn't she an adult?!</b>

6
00:09:41.206 --> 00:09:42.958
<b>- So you don't care what happens to her?
- --I didn't say that!</b>

7
00:09:43.041 --> 00:09:44.126
<b>That's what it sounds like!</b>

8
00:09:44.209 --> 00:09:45.335
<b>Now isn't the damn time--</b>

9
00:09:45.419 --> 00:09:47.379
<b>Don't talk to your father like that.</b>

10
00:18:13.802 --> 00:18:16.847
<b>He wants to make his father proud…</b>

11
00:18:17.472 --> 00:18:18.807
<b>I am.</b>

12
00:18:21.518 --> 00:18:22.978
<b>But…</b>

13
00:18:24.897 --> 00:18:26.231
<b>Does he know that?</b>

14
00:39:35.125 --> 00:39:36.919
<b>Hiroshi. are you ready?</b>

15
00:39:37.753 --> 00:39:38.837
<b>It's time to go!</b>

16
00:39:58.232 --> 00:39:59.525
<b>We're going on a plane.</b>

17
00:40:01.818 --> 00:40:03.570
<b>A big one!</b>

